'''TIE hangar bay 62-N9''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] aboard [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star I]] used as a docking bay for [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]]. This hangar featured a TIE hangar rack capable of holding up to seventy-two TIE fighters in individual, ceiling-mounted berths. It was destroyed in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

